                "activityType": "notes",
                "title": "Assignment",
                "text": "MSIT Wants to embed a Quiz section in LMS PORTAL, for this you need to develop a front-end application by using the technologies mentioned.<ol type=\"a\"><li>HTML</li><li>CSS</li><li>Javascript</li><li>AJAX</li><li>JSON</li></ol><p>You need to develop a single page Quiz application, where you need a quiz environment, where a student can enter his roll no, course and be able to answer the quiz questions.You need to create a quiz with a timer to close the quiz after the allotted time.For loading the quiz questions dynamically use AJAX to  fetch quiz data  from a JSON file that has been stored in your github repository and render the questions.</p><p>After clicking the Submit button / timer runs out,  you need to evaluate the quiz answers and print the result on the same page.</p><p>For reference of the quiz environment use a Socrative portal as a reference one and prepare your own customized Quiz portal.</p><p></p>Evaluation Criteria:(80)<ol><li>Creation of Quiz<ol type=\"a\"><li>HTML-10</li><li>CSS & User look and feel - 20</li><li>Javascript-10</li><li>JSON -10</li><li>Ajax - 20</li><li>Printing Result - 10</li></ol></li></ol><b>Submission guidelines:</b><br>Every student should submit the assignment by uploading into drive or github. Please submit it in <a href=\"https://submit.msitprogram.net/courses/IT-Workshop/assessments/explorehtmltags\" target=\"_blank\">Autolab</a> by pasting the drive or github(along with commit id)  URL in a text file with a naming convention as “yourrollnumber_yourname.txt”. The deadline for the assignment is the next day at 9AM."
